### LearningArticle API Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:5085

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5085
@articleId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@moduleId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### 1. Get All Learning Articles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learningarticles

### 2. Get Learning Article by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learningarticles/{{articleId}}

### 3. Get Learning Articles by Module ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learningarticles/module/{{moduleId}}

### 4. Create Simple Learning Article
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learningarticles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "learningModuleId": "{{moduleId}}",
  "contentItems": []
}

### 5. Create Learning Article with Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learningarticles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "learningModuleId": "{{moduleId}}",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "content": "This is the introduction to the article.",
      "sectionBlockNumber": 1
    },
    {
      "content": "This is the main content section with detailed information.",
      "sectionBlockNumber": 2
    },
    {
      "content": "This is the conclusion section.",
      "sectionBlockNumber": 3
    }
  ]
}

### 6. Update Learning Article
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/learningarticles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{articleId}}",
  "learningModuleId": "{{moduleId}}",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "content": "Updated introduction content.",
      "sectionBlockNumber": 1
    },
    {
      "content": "Updated main content with new information.",
      "sectionBlockNumber": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 7. Delete Learning Article
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/learningarticles/{{articleId}}

